 bits & Tours,Guided Tours
DESCRIPTION:Guided tours of Fort Macon are available daily at 1:00 p.m. dur
 ing the Park's slower season between mid Oct. and Mid April.\n\nThe tours w
 ill last about 45 minutes.\n\nMeet at the fort entrance. Pets are not allow
 ed inside the fort.\n\n \n\nPhoto by C. Peek: The fort at Fort Macon State 
 Park
