BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Exhibits & Tours,Guided Tours
DESCRIPTION:Learn about some of the remarkable women who lived and worked a
 t Somerset Place. The 60- minute special tour will focus on the contributio
 ns that enslaved and free women made to the development\, maintenance\, and
  infrastructure of Somerset Place. The tour will be offered to commemorate 
 Women’s History Month. Guided tour fees of $10.00 per person applicable and
  for 15 or more group reservations are required.
DTEND:20260311T150000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030915Z
DTSTART:20260311T140000Z
GEO:35.789477;-76.404637
LOCATION:Somerset Place
SEQUENCE:0
