DESCRIPTION:Climb aboard our St. Patrick’s Train on the evenings of March 1
 3 & 14 and enjoy an Irish-inspired meal while riding the rails at the N.C. 
 Transportation Museum. Wear your green and bring your Irish cheer! This din
 ner train will offer guests a happy hour of live music\, appetizers\, wine\
 , and beer before boarding the train. Dinner will be served as you roll dow
 n the tracks\, enjoying a full Irish-inspired meal!\n\nAdvance ticket purch
 ase is strongly recommended. For members of the museum\, it is strongly enc
 ouraged to reserve tickets in advance using your membership number.\n\nEach
  individual passenger will receive two drink tickets to be redeemed from ou
 r selection of wine and beer in either the cocktail area or on the train. A
 dditional drinks can also be purchased for an additional cost.\n\nThis even
 t is for ages 21 and up only. There is no admittance for anyone under age 2
 1. Valid ID must be shown.
DTEND:20260315T003000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030916Z
DTSTART:20260314T203000Z
GEO:35.687243;-80.433348
LOCATION:North Carolina Transportation Museum
SEQUENCE:0
