DESCRIPTION:Join a Park Ranger on a half-mile hike to seek out signs of spr
 ing at the park. This scavenger hunt trek will utilize the senses and requi
 re a sense of curiosity as well! We will look high and low for ways to disc
 over nature as it wakes up from the long and hard winter\, focusing on obse
 rving the changing colors\, textures\, and sounds of the season. Please dre
 ss for the weather. Registration is required and please email Ranger Baker 
 to sign up: lindsey.baker@ncparks.gov.
DTEND:20260317T150000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030916Z
