 ton-ladies-tea-party
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Education Programs,Workshops & Trainings
DESCRIPTION:Two Designers\, one design space. Share the beautiful and quirk
 y world of Jennifer Wood and Francisco Garcia\, owners of Once Gathered\, a
  wedding and event florist based in Morrisville\, NC. Watch as this husband
 -and-wife team demonstrates making an arrangement with the same materials a
 nd ends at completely different results!\n\nThis demonstration touches on u
 nique floral varieties\, seasonality\, styles of floral design\, and Wood a
 nd Garcia’s love story with each other and their profession. Additionally\,
  both designers bring premade arrangements and discuss technique\, movement
 \, shape\, and color. Watching these two chatter about running a floral com
 pany is sure to educate\, entertain\, and delight.\n\n \n\n$44\, Members $4
 0
DTEND:20260318T173000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030917Z
DTSTART:20260318T160000Z
