  be familiar with. This will be March's new moon so expect it to be darker 
 than some nights. \n\nMeeting location is at the Mayo Mountain Access parki
 ng lot. The Mayo Mountain Loop is an easy 2 mile hike. Please bring hiking 
 shoes\, a jacket\, water\, and a flash light. \n\nIf you have further quest
 ions\, please call the park office at (336) 916-6080. \n\nPlease note: This
  event is subject to cancellation due to weather. \n\nPhoto source: Tom Ran
