DESCRIPTION:Join local bestselling author and horticulturist Brie Arthur fo
 r an engaging journey into the art of container gardening! Learn how to des
 ign\, plant\, and care for containers that bring beauty\, productivity\, an
 d year-round interest to any space.\n\nThis lively session includes demonst
 rations of step-by-step techniques for soil\, fertilizer\, plant selection\
 , layering\, and creative combinations. Whether you’re gardening on a balco
 ny\, patio\, or in a small yard\, Arthur provides practical tips\, inspirat
 ion\, and insider secrets to make your containers flourish. You’ll be ready
  to roll up your sleeves and watch your garden ideas come to life!\n\nNo fo
 od is provided\, but you may bring light refreshments to enjoy quietly thro
 ughout the program.
