DESCRIPTION:This monthly journaling series offers attendees a chance to slo
 w down from life’s complexities and notice the subtle details that nature p
 rovides—sunlight on leaves\, birdsong\, changing weather—and to capture the
 se moments on paper through words or images. This month’s journal entry foc
 uses on mindfulness. Bring your journal and something to write with. We'll 
 meet at the Live Oak loop. Program is weather dependent.
