 Special Site Programs,Outdoor & Recreation,Outdoor Recreation (kayak, paddl
 e, hikes),Nature & Wildlife Programs,Youth & Family Activities
DESCRIPTION:Join the Curious Minds Adventure Scavenger Hunt at Elk Knob Sta
 te Park. Journey through northern hardwood forest\, follow winding mountain
  trails\, and explore the unique ecosystems of this high-elevation park. Ke
 ep your eyes open—what signs of wildlife or weather-shaped landscapes will 
 you uncover? Look for unique rocks that make Elk Knob a very special clue i
 n North Carolina’s geologic history. Start at the Visitor Center and scan t
 he QR code in your Actionbound app. Flyers with the QR code will be placed 
 in the Park Office and on all park map kiosks. \n\nThe adventures are avail
 able on the Actionbound app – a free download to your cellphone through you
 r phone’s app store. There’s no need to create a profile and no personal da
 ta is collected with Actionbound. You simply find new hunts by searching fo
 r the park name or scanning the associated QR code posted for your park’s a
 dventure.\n\nThis program is made possible through a partnership with the N
 C Science Trail (ncsciencetrail.org)! Visit their website for more Curious 
 Minds Adventure Scavenger Hunts being held in other NC State Parks and for 
 other programs being offered throughout the state. \n\nThis scavenger hunt 
 is running now through April 30\, 2026.
DTEND:20260329T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030920Z
DTSTART:20260328T110000Z
GEO:36.333462;-81.696432
LOCATION:Elk Knob State Park
SEQUENCE:0
