DESCRIPTION:This workshop designed by Maureen O’Neill offers a variety of e
 xercises to help participants connect to and engage with the present moment
 . Through guided mark making (drawing and painting)\, participants learn to
  shift focus to their touch and breath and experience how a beautiful line 
 or color can bring them into a meditative place that is both healing and cr
 eative.\n\nSupplies are included and no art experience is necessary. This w
 orkshop encourages and supports the strength and wisdom of the intuitive sp
 irit.\n\nCost: $50\, Members $40
