X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Celebrations & Commemorations,Reenactments & Living History,Exhi
 bits & Tours,Special Site Programs
DESCRIPTION:History is most definitely not a black and white subject! From 
 costly indigo from the tropics to humble madder roots from the Mediterranea
 n\, explore the dyestuffs that helped fuel global economies and bring color
  to our lives.\n\nThis event is part of the museum’s Deep Dive Into History
  series\, programs designed to give visitors a deeper understanding of our 
 shared past through costumed interpretation. Each Deep Dive delves into a s
 pecific theme in Lower Cape Fear and maritime history. Programs run from 11
  a.m. to 3 p.m.\, and visitors can interact one-on-one with the presenter a
 t any time during the program.
DTEND:20260328T190000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030920Z
DTSTART:20260328T150000Z
