DESCRIPTION:Take a behind the scenes tour of the Vance Birthplace and disco
 ver the story of Elizabeth Hemphill!\n\nElizabeth and her post office becam
 e the center of Vanceville\, a community that developed in the Reems Creek 
 Valley after the Vances moved to Asheville in the 1840s. Uncover her story 
 and explore our artifact collection on this behind the scenes tour of the V
 ance house.\n\nTickets are $10 per person. Register in person or online at 
 Zeffy. Tours are 90 minutes and will take place at 11:00 am and 1:00 pm. If
  you have any questions\, feel free to reach out via email at vance@dncr.nc
 .gov or by phone at (828) 645-6706!
