DESCRIPTION:Come and explore one of Eno River State Park's best locations f
 or wildflowers! Join a Park Ranger and find out what's in bloom in the earl
 y Spring and some fun facts about our early wildflower emergers.\n\nAll chi
 ldren must be accompanied by an adult. Please be sure to dress appropriatel
 y for the weather\, wear hiking shoes\, and bring water!\n\nSpaces are limi
 ted\, and registration is required. To sign up\, call (984) 250-1370 or ema
 il eno.river@ncparks.gov. Include the number of guests in your party and a 
 phone number where you can be reached if the event is changed or canceled.
