 Outdoor & Recreation,Outdoor Recreation (kayak, paddle, hikes),Nature & Wil
 dlife Programs,Youth & Family Activities
DESCRIPTION:A master of camouflage\, the American Woodcock\, also known as 
 the Timber Doodle\, is a fascinating bird with a unique mating call and fli
 ght pattern.  Meet a Park Ranger at the picnic area at Elk Knob State Park 
 to find out more details about this unique\, little bird.  This program is 
 open to all ages.
DTEND:20260331T234500Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030921Z
