DESCRIPTION:Embark on the Curious Minds Adventure Scavenger Hunt at Lake Ja
 mes State Park! Located in Burke and McDowell counties 50 miles northeast o
 f Asheville\, Lake James State Park includes two areas to access this pictu
 resque lake that are perfect for boating\, swimming\, and fishing. Campsite
 s at both Catawba River and Paddy's Creek accesses provide an opportunity t
 o spend the night by the lake\, with some sites accessible only by paddling
 . Trails include bike trails at Paddy's Creek\, the kid-friendly Holly Disc
 overy Trail\, the historic Overmountain Victory Trail\, and the Fonta Flora
  State Trail.
DTEND:20260403T230000Z
