DESCRIPTION:Join Ranger Gracie at the Pilot Creek access for a beginner-fri
 endly bird walk to discover the birds that call Pilot Mountain State Park h
 ome. We'll take a leisurely walk along park trails while learning how to sp
 ot and identify common birds by sight and sound. This program is perfect fo
 r first-time birders and for all ages. No experience or equipment needed\, 
 but if you have binoculars\, bring them! Please RSVP by emailing pilot.moun
 tain@ncparks.gov.
