DESCRIPTION:Travel back to 1770s–1780s Cumberland County\, North Carolina\,
  when tensions are rising and the American colonies are on the brink of rev
 olution. In this immersive tabletop role-playing game\, you’ll step into th
 e shoes of local citizens navigating loyalty\, rebellion and survival durin
 g a pivotal moment in history.\n\nExplore real historical events\, regional
  battles and political intrigue as you make choices that shape your story. 
 Will you side with the Patriots\, remain loyal to the Crown or try to survi
 ve somewhere in between?\n\nNo prior role-playing experience is necessary—j
 ust bring your imagination and your sense of adventure.\n\nRegistration is 
 required by calling 910-483-7727\, ext. 1365\, or registering online.
DTEND:20260410T003000Z
