DESCRIPTION:Join us and Alex Brown\, director of programs and audience enga
 gement at NCMA Winston-Salem\, for a virtual sensory journey inspired by Al
 ison Saar’s Tippy Toes.  \n\nDuring this hour-long program\, participants a
 re prompted to use kit items to activate the senses of touch\, taste\, smel
 l\, and sound. Paired with audio description\, this immersive sensory exper
 ience fosters a deep\, personal connection to the featured artwork.  \n\nPa
 rticipants are mailed a small sensory kit free of charge\; limited to one k
 it per household. \n\nRegistration closes Friday\, March 27.
