 om the 17th and 18th centuries on period instruments. Be sure to stop by an
 d enjoy their performance.\n\nEnjoy a variety of spring blooming plants\, i
 ncluding tulips\, irises\, and more\, throughout the 21 acres of gardens of
  Tryon Palace during Garden Lovers’ Weekend. \n\nBe sure to visit the Sprin
 g Heritage Plant Sale while you’re there!\n\nInterior tours require the pur
 chase of a ticket.
