  to increase biodiversity and provide habitat for wildlife. \n\nIncludes wa
 lking up to a mile total on paved and grassy surfaces with slight inclines 
 as well as lifting\, bending\, and digging. Ages 14 and up. \n\nPark servic
 e projects occur twice a year\, weather permitting\, in fall and spring.
