DESCRIPTION:Join us during Spring Garden Lovers’ Weekend as Tryon Palace ho
 sts the “Skirmish at Tryon Palace” fencing tournament on the South Lawn! Bo
 uts will commence throughout the day starting at 10 A.M. when the grounds o
 pen.\n\nWhether you’re a fencing enthusiast or just looking for a fun way t
 o spend your Saturday\, this will be a fun event for the whole family. To m
 ake it even better\, viewing the tournament will be free and open to public
  along with with Palace Grounds and Gardens during the event weekend!\n\nYo
 u can also check out the Spring Heritage Plant Sale on the grounds by the D
 aves House. It’s a great opportunity to find some plants you won’t find in 
 other retail locations and to purchase plants that are from the Tryon Palac
 e Gardens.\n\nPalace tours and admission to certain locations and exhibits 
 will require a ticket purchase.
