  North Carolina Symphony for the purely magnificent Mozart Mass. \n\nNorth 
 Carolina SymphonyCarlos Miguel Prieto\, conductor Amanda Forsythe\, soprano
  Mei Gui Zhang\, soprano Issachah Savage\, tenor Harold Wilson\, bass North
  Carolina Master Chorale Arrive early for Concert Insights to join Music Di
 rector Carlos Miguel Prieto\, who will describe highlights of the music (ev
 ening concerts only). This free 30-minute pre-concert event begins at 7PM (
 Friday & Saturday)  in the concert hall.
