CATEGORIES:Education Programs,Workshops & Trainings
DESCRIPTION:Join the North Carolina Arts Council and A+ Schools of North Ca
 rolina for a FREE\, engaging\, hands-on professional development session de
 signed for ANY PreK-8 educator! Explore how arts integration with music and
  visual arts can enhance student learning across all subjects and bring new
  energy to your classroom. Participants will receive a certificate of atten
 dance. This interactive workshop will feature model lessons\, collaborative
  activities\, and practical strategies you can apply immediately. You’ll al
 so learn about additional professional development and resources available 
 through N.C. Arts Council and A+ Schools to support arts integration in you
 r school. \n\nLunch providedLimited scholarships to cover sub costs are ava
 ilableRegistration is due by 5:00 PM on March 25.
DTEND:20260413T190000Z
