 he 250th Anniversary of the Declaration of Independence. Meet the Revolutio
 nary War Figures of North Carolina representing all aspects and viewpoints 
 from the Revolution through an interactive living wax museum as well as a h
 istory row with representatives from Colonial and Revolutionary War Sites a
 nd Organizations from across North Carolina!
