DESCRIPTION:Join us at NC Freedom Park as local students share information 
 about the voices represented in NC Freedom Park\, after spending the past s
 emester researching the notable Black North Carolinians honored in the park
 . Additional student-created works\, including paintings\, poems\, digital 
 art\, and other creative interpretations inspired by the park’s honorees\, 
 will also be on display. A Jazz Band will perform music by North Carolina c
 omposers such as Thelonious Monk\, John Coltrane\, and Nina Simone.
