CATEGORIES:Performances & Arts,Spoken Word/Readings,Education Programs,Lect
 ures & Talks,Celebrations & Commemorations,Ceremonies & Anniversaries,Organ
 izational
DESCRIPTION:The first flight by the Wright Brothers on the Outer Banks was 
 a defining moment for Dare County\, accelerating Dare County's growth with 
 the construction of the Wright Brothers Memorial Bridge just a few years af
 ter the 25th Anniversary of the first flight underscored how isolated the O
 uter Banks were. The Wright Brothers are an important component of American
  History\, certainly something that should be celebrated on the 250th Anniv
 ersary.\n\n \n\nEvent Highlights:\n\nRecognition of sponsors and partners c
 ontributing to the First Flight Society.\n\nSilent auction featuring signed
  items from FFS Honorary Members and generous sponsor donations.\n\nAll pro
 ceeds from the auction support First Flight Society programs.\n\n \n\nTicke
 t cost: $50
DTEND:20260417T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030923Z
DTSTART:20260416T220000Z
GEO:35.910067;-75.595585
LOCATION:Jennette's Pier
SEQUENCE:0
