LOCATION:North Carolina Aquarium at Pine Knoll Shores
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Shorebird Bird Hike
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_52384043768498
URL:https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/shorebird-bird-hike
