X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Education Programs,Lectures & Talks
DESCRIPTION:Tryon Palace is excited to welcome back Dr. Antwain K. Hunter t
 o the North Carolina History Center!\n\nExplore the fragile and uncertain r
 ealities faced by African Americans navigating freedom. Participants will c
 onsider how individuals and communities balanced resistance\, adaptation\, 
 and hope while living within structures that could shift at any moment. Thr
 ough historical analysis and discussion\, the lecture invites audiences to 
 reflect on how this delicate balance shaped the pursuit of dignity\, citize
 nship\, and freedom.
DTEND:20260418T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030923Z
DTSTART:20260417T220000Z
