DESCRIPTION:Join us for a relaxing morning fishing program at Lake James St
 ate Park – Catawba River Access\, perfect for families and first-time angle
 rs alike! Bring your kids\, your favorite fishing rods\, and any tackle you
  have—we’ll also have a limited number of rods and tackle available to loan
 .\n\nWe’ll meet at the picnic shelter\, then head together to the jetty\, w
 here there’s plenty of space to spread out and fish. Spend the morning enjo
 ying the calm water\, learning a few fishing tips\, and sharing quality tim
 e with loved ones while making lasting memories—plus\, you just might reel 
 in a fish or two!\n\nWhether you’re teaching your child to fish for the fir
 st time or simply enjoying a peaceful morning outdoors\, this program is a 
 great way to connect with nature and each other.\n\nAll ages welcome. No ex
 perience necessary! All NCWRC Laws must be followed such as having a valid 
 NC fishing license.🎣
DTEND:20260418T140000Z
