DESCRIPTION:Our spring native plant sale is one of the most anticipated eve
 nts of the year for the Umstead community. This year's sale features over 2
 0 locally grown native species\, including perennials\, shrubs\, grasses\, 
 ferns\, and trees.\n\nPopular species go quickly — Umstead Coalition member
 s and donors receive early entry from 11am to noon. The best way to guarant
 ee first pick is to become a member or make a donation of $15 or more befor
 e April 18.
