DESCRIPTION:Don’t miss your chance to be part of history!\n\nWe’re hosting 
 a dedication celebration for the America250 Guilford County Time Capsule!\n
 \nSaturday\, April 18\n\n2:00 pm – 4:00 pm\n\nHigh Point Museum\n\n \n\nThe
  event will include the dedication ceremony\, an artifact display\, light r
 efreshments\, family activities\, reenactors\, and more.\n\nArtifacts will 
 be held in the High Point Historical Society Collections at the High Point 
 Museum to be opened in 2076.\n\n \n\nWe are collecting artifacts through th
 e end of the year for potential inclusion. If you have a donation for consi
 deration\, please fill out the form at: america250guilford.com/time-capsule
 -donations/\n\nFor questions about the event or donations\, please visit th
 e High Point Museum or America250 Guilford’s websites.
