 es
DESCRIPTION:Join us at Mayo River State Park for a Spring Flower Potting ev
 ent! We will be gathering at the Mayo Mountain shelter with mini planting p
 ots\, soil\, and seeds for participants to plant their own flowers for spri
 ng. This program is tailored for families with kids so they can experience 
 that exciting responsibility of growing their own flower for spring. \n\nGl
 oves are welcome if participants prefer\nWe will have Cardinal Flower\, Ora
 nge Coneflower\, and American Beauty-berry seeds optional for potting.
DTEND:20260420T210000Z
