DESCRIPTION:Join Ranger Austin for a monring paddle on the Roanoke Sound.  
 Learn more about the aquatic side of Jockey's Ridge.  Discussion will also 
 include park ecology and natural/cultural history.  All equipment will be p
 rovided to include instruction.  Minimum participant age is 8 years-old.  C
 hildren under 13 must paddle with an adult (18 or older). \n\nPre-registrat
 ion is required.  Please email austin.paul@ncparksgov to sign up.  Include 
 the names of all participants\, ages\, and a contact phone number.  \n\nPle
 ase arrive at least 10 minutes early.\n\nLocation:  330 W Soundside Road\, 
 Nags Head\, NC 27959
