 come. This is a weather-dependent event as cloud cover can interfere with v
 iewing. Please call the visitor center a few days prior for updates. Regist
 ration is not required.  \n\nFriday\, April 24th and 25th \n\nSolar Viewing
 : 10 am to 12 pm (only on 25th)\n\nNighttime Viewing: 8:00 pm to 9:00 pm (b
 oth 24th and 25th)\n\nLocation: Visitor Center Parking Lot
