 ! Telescopes will be set up for public viewing. Space based arts and craft 
 table activities for kids will be available from 5:30pm until dark\, night 
 sky viewing until 10:00pm (weather permitting). This free outdoor event is 
 brought to you thanks to NC Science Festival\, Friends of Jockey’s Ridge\, 
 OBX Astronomy Club\, Back Bay Amateur Astronomers\, Dare County Library\, a
 nd all of our wonderful volunteers. All are welcome! Event subject to cance
 llation depending on inclement weather.
