BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Performances & Arts,Concerts (Music)
DESCRIPTION:Kick back\, relax\, and let us provide the soundtrack to a hang
 out with your favorite people. The iQ is partnering with NCMA Winston-Salem
  to bring their House Hangs series outdoors to Bailey Park. Aptly renamed P
 ark Hangs\, this reinvented Signature Event series features talented musici
 ans at the Bailey Park stage in the midst of the iQ’s iconic cityscape. Get
  ready for the opportunity to enjoy music and socialize at this laid-back c
 ommunity event.  \n\nEvent Details\n\nPark Hangs will bring free live music
  to the iQ once a month from April through October. To make sure everyone c
 an comfortably enjoy the performance\, please plan to bring a blanket to si
 t on or a low-backed outdoor chair. Dogs are welcome\, but they must remain
  leashed for the duration of the event.\n\nFood and Beverage Vendors\n\nA r
 otating selection of food trucks and drink vendors will be at all Park Hang
 s events. Additionally\, you’re welcome to bring your own food to the park 
 or carry in food from one of your favorite iQ restaurants during the event.
  Drinks from Incendiary Brewing will be available for purchase\, but outsid
 e alcohol is prohibited.\n\nEvent Time\n\nEach Park Hangs concert will be h
 eld from 6-8 p.m. Food and drink will be available to purchase starting an 
 hour before the event. \n\nLocation\n\nParks Hangs takes place on the Upper
  Lawn of Bailey Park\, 445 Patterson Ave. Winston-Salem\, NC\n\nParking\n\n
 Limited street parking is available for this event\, with additional paid p
 arking in the Link Parking Deck located at 530 North Patterson Avenue.\n\nW
 eather Plan\n\nIn the event of inclement weather\, an announcement about ca
 ncellation or rescheduling will be made by 4 p.m. on the day of the event.
DTEND:20260425T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030925Z
DTSTART:20260424T220000Z
GEO:36.099537;-80.240911
LOCATION:Bailey Park\, Upper Lawn
SEQUENCE:0
