DESCRIPTION:Join us on Saturday April 25th\, 2026\, from 7:00pm to 9:00pm a
 t Morrow Mountain State Park for the Statewide Star Party! We’ll have activ
 ities focusing on our theme\, “Mission to the Moon\,” and stargazing. Repre
 sentatives from the Charlotte Amateur Astronomers Club\, as well as local a
 stronomers\, will be standing by to answer questions and allow peeks throug
 h some high-powered telescopes! Meet in the large parking lot adjacent to o
 ur swimming pool. Participants are encouraged to bring telescopes and binoc
 ulars. Please try to limit light pollution once it gets dark. See you there
 ! Rain date: Saturday May 2nd\, 2026. The NC Science Festival’s annual Stat
 ewide Star Party is made possible through the generous support of the NC Sp
 ace Grant More information can be found here: https://ncsciencefestival.org
 /events/statewide-star-party-morrow-mountain-state-park/
