DESCRIPTION:Join Ranger Marissa in the picnic area to make different nature
  observations! From different trees\, flowers\, fungi\, and animals\, we wi
 ll be looking at it all! Nature journals and craft materials will be availa
 ble to all participants so that we can draw and write about our findings as
  we go. This program will also give participants the opportunity to earn a 
 NC Bioblitz patch or sticker from Science Across NC. This program is open t
 o all ages.
