DESCRIPTION:We all huddled inside through a cold winter\, but how did the t
 urtles stay warm during the snow and ice? Learn all about turtle superpower
 s that help them survive the winter months!\n\nAll children must be accompa
 nied by an adult. Please be sure to dress appropriately for the weather\, w
 ear hiking shoes\, and bring water!\n\nSpaces are limited\, and registratio
 n is required. To sign up\, call (984) 250-1370 or email eno.river@ncparks.
 gov. Include the number of guests in your party and a phone number where yo
 u can be reached if the event is changed or canceled.
