DESCRIPTION:Please join us for the April meeting of the America 250 NC Virt
 ual Book Club! We will be discussing Cold Mountain by Charles Frazier on Ap
 ril 29th at 6p.\n\nThis historical fiction novel explores the Civil War in 
 North Carolina and the human impact of battle. \n\nPlease read the book pri
 or to the discussion. We recommend borrowing from your local library. \n\nF
 ree and open to the public. No membership required. Come to whichever book 
 talks spark your interest. \n\nMeeting Link\n\nMore Information\n\nSign up 
 for an Email Reminder
