  area in a classroom setting. Afterwards\, we'll go into the field to obser
 ve local butterflies. You will also learn about the Carolinas Butterfly Mon
 itoring Program and how you can participate in this citizen science project
 . This course will be taught by Jeff Pippen\, Director of the CBMP.
