DESCRIPTION:Since 1811 the Old Wilkesboro Presbyterian Church Cemetery\, lo
 cated at 299 E. South Street in Wilkesboro\, NC 28697\, has served as a fin
 al resting place for loved ones. Join the Rendezvous Mountain Chapter of th
 e National Society Daughters of the American Revolution (RMC NSDAR)\, the T
 own of Wilkesboro\, and your community as we serve together to honor our an
 cesters\, preserve history\, educate the next generation\, and show patriot
 ism as we celebrate the 250th birthday of America.\n\nWe invite you and you
 r family members to team up with our knowledgeable preservationists to unve
 il the historic headstones that algae\, lichen\, weather\, and erosion have
  hidden.\n\nIf you would like more information about this event\, please co
 ntact the Rendezvous Mountain Chapter\, NSDAR at: https:/www.ncdar.org/Rend
 ezvousMt
DTEND:20260502T190000Z
