DESCRIPTION:Come learn about the Library's upcoming America 250 mural from 
 artist Max Dowdle\, and then try your hand at your own mural drawing! Can y
 ou create your own mural to celebrate America? What famous Americans would 
 you include?\n\nThis project was produced with assistance from the America 
 250 North Carolina initiative\, administered by the North Carolina Departme
