DESCRIPTION:Join Mayo River State Park for our annual FAMILY FISHING DAY! A
  fun-filled day with lots of activities for the whole family.\n\nOn-site RE
 GISTRATION begins at 9:00am at MAYO MOUNTAIN ACCESS\, 500 Old Mayo Park Roa
 d\, Mayodan\, NC 27027. FISHING DERBY with prizes in age-appropriate catego
 ries for participants 16 years and younger. All children must be ACCOMPANIE
 D BY AN ADULT who will be in the park and supervising them at all times. PR
 IZES awarded around 2:00pm. The day is also a LICENSE-EXEMPT fishing day fo
 r adults.\n\nBRING YOUR OWN bait/tackle\, extra drinking water/snacks\, sun
 screen and bug repellent. FREE hot dogs\, chips and drinks while they last.
  DIY WORKSHOP for kids.\n\nJoin us for a NATURALLY WONDERFUL day in the par
 k! For more information call the park office at 336-427-2530.
DTEND:20260506T180000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030927Z
DTSTART:20260506T130000Z
GEO:36.439192;-79.948638
LOCATION:Mayo River State Park\, Mayo Mountain Access
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Family Fishing Day
