DESCRIPTION:Historian and author Bob Plott will discuss lesser-known causes
  of unrest in the Carolina colonies\, beginning as early as 1761\, featurin
 g British generals\, freed slaves\, American frontiersmen\, and iconic Cher
 okee warriors and chiefs—drawn from his books and other sources — for an en
 gaging blend of education and entertainment. It is a program you will not w
 ant to miss. This event is sponsored by the Transylvania Heritage Museum.
