DESCRIPTION:What’s cooler than absolute zero? The answer is Science Trivia 
 night at NCMNS!\n\nQuestions feature a mix of science facts\, current news\
 , pop culture and scientific discoveries. Held in the Daily Planet Cafe the
  first Thursday of each month\, this is a great opportunity to mingle with 
