BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Education Programs,Workshops & Trainings,Lectures & Talks
DESCRIPTION:This year is America's 250th anniversary\, but how do you find 
 your Revolutionary ancestors? Could you be a Son of the American Revolution
  and not know it? Join us for a virtual presentation by Scott Norrick of An
 cestral Past\, where you will learn practical tips on finding potential rev
 olutionary ancestors. \n\nThis project was produced with assistance from th
 e America 250 North Carolina initiative\, administered by the North Carolin
 a Department of Natural and Cultural Resources. Any opinions\, findings\, a
 nd conclusions or recommendations expressed in this material are those of t
 he author(s) and do not necessarily reflect the views of the State of North
  Carolina.
DTEND:20260513T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030927Z
DTSTART:20260512T230000Z
LOCATION:
