BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Exhibits & Tours,Special Site Programs
DESCRIPTION:Gather up your Fellowship as the Museum becomes Middle Earth fo
 r a night. Lay siege to Gondor\, dance with dragons and show off your Tolki
 en trivia at this adults 21+ event.\n\nEnjoy a unique opportunity to experi
 ence the Museum at night while exploring the uncensored side of science. Th
 e event features interactive science stations\, music\, games\, local enter
 tainment and special activities. Beer\, wine\, themed cocktails and food wi
 ll be available for purchase. Costumes encouraged (but not required).\n\nTi
 ckets: $25\; $15 Members. You must be 21 years or older to attend. A photo 
 ID is required for entry.\n\nCOSTUME POLICY\n\nGuests wearing masks must re
 move them during check-in. They can then wear them during the event.Footwea
 r is required.Outfits should not contain elements that resemble or could be
  mistaken for a real weapon.We reserve the right to refuse a guest wearing 
 a costume deemed offensive or unsafe.Any face or body paint must not obscur
 e an attendee’s identity.
DTEND:20260516T020000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030927Z
DTSTART:20260515T223000Z
