BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Outdoor & Recreation,Nature & Wildlife Programs
DESCRIPTION:Join us and the Crystal Coast Stargazers at the beach access / 
 bathhouse parking area to view space through a telescope and learn more abo
 ut our universe.\n\nThis event is dependent on clear weather and may be can
 celed due to rain or heavy cloud cover. If you have a telescope\, feel free
  to bring it. Pets are not permitted at this program. \n\nIf you are not se
 tting up equipment for observations we ask that you park in the west parkin
 g lot as you first enter\, then walk across to the east lot for the program
 .  This helps reduce the amount of bright lights in the observation area fr
 om headlights. \n\n \n\nPhoto by P. Terry: Star trails over a cannon at For
 t Macon State Park
DTEND:20260516T010000Z
