DESCRIPTION:James and Nancy Bennett lived along the Hillsborough Road\, a m
 ajor throughway between the county seat of Hillsborough and the state capit
 al of Raleigh. They made money by selling goods & services to passers-by on
  the roadway.\n\nOn May 16\, Bennett Place State Historic Site brings back 
 that entrepreneurial\, small-business spirit with the Old Hillsborough Road
  Market. Shop local craft\, retail\, and food vendors while exploring our h
 istoric site! The program also features historic trades demonstrations and 
 free ranger-talks in the Bennett home.\n\n \n\nVendors wanted! Please conta
 ct us for more information about registration requirements.
DTEND:20260516T190000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030928Z
