BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Exhibits & Tours,Guided Tours
DESCRIPTION:Step into Tryon Palace and explore Diana Gabaldon’s award-winni
 ng Outlander series. Learn about the lives of the fictional Jamie and Clair
 e Fraser\, their family and friends\, and interactions with historical figu
 res and events in the tumultuous period of the American Revolution.\n\nTour
  covers storylines from Outlander books 4 – 8 and the Starz Outlander seaso
 ns 4 – 8. (For those not current on the books or show\, there will be spoil
 ers for these books and seasons.)\n\nTour begins at 301 George Street\, acr
 oss from the Tryon Palace Main Gates. Ticket holders should check in at the
  Waystation ticketing desk no later than 3:30 p.m.
DTEND:20260516T204500Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030928Z
DTSTART:20260516T194500Z
GEO:35.104831;-77.043044
LOCATION:Tryon Palace Historic Sites and Gardens
SEQUENCE:0
