BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Exhibits & Tours,Exhibitions
DESCRIPTION:KMHM is excited to present Women at the Edge of War: Carolina P
 iedmont's Heroines of the American Revolution. This exhibit highlights the 
 daily courage and civic work of women in the Carolinas\, whose efforts were
  essential to Revolutionary resistance and survival on the southern frontie
 r.\n\nThe exhibit will run from Feb. 17\, 2026 to May 30\, 2026. The museum
  is open Tues-Sat\, 10-4. Admission is free. Check out kingsmountainmuseum.
 org or call 704-739-1019 for more information.
DTEND:20260519T200000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030928Z
DTSTART:20260519T140000Z
GEO:35.239004;-81.342181
LOCATION:Kings Mountain Historical Museum
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Women at the Edge of War: Carolina Piedmont's Heroines of the Ameri
 can Revolution
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51878259899686
URL:https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/women-at-the-edge-of-war-carolina-pied
 monts-heroines-of-the-american-revolution
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Education Programs,Lectures & Talks
DESCRIPTION:This presentation will shift the focus away from the Cumberland
  Association signers themselves to talk about the women in their lives. We 
 will discuss the women's experiences during the Revolutionary War\, from en
 emy threats to cunning rescues\, and even their experiences after the war.\
 n\nThis project was produced with assistance from the America 250 North Car
 olina initiative\, administered by the North Carolina Department of Natural
  and Cultural Resources. Any opinions\, findings and conclusions or recomme
 ndations expressed in this material are those of the author(s) and do not n
 ecessarily reflect the views of the State of North Carolina.
DTEND:20260519T200000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030928Z
DTSTART:20260519T190000Z
GEO:35.055443;-78.881263
LOCATION:Cumberland County Public Library\, Local & State History Room
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Women of the Liberty Point Resolves
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_52428579347534
URL:https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/women-of-the-liberty-point-resolves
END:VEVENT
