X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Education Programs,Lectures & Talks
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a journey into the past presented by local historia
 n Dr. Roger Roark. Discover the pivotal role played by Governor Arthur Dobb
 s and the strategic significance of Fort Dobbs during the French and Indian
  War.
