X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Celebrations & Commemorations
DESCRIPTION:Remember those who gave their lives in service by honoring vete
 rans at the Battleship’s 61st Memorial Day Observance featuring a special g
 uest military speaker\, the 4th Fighter Wing Honor Guard from Seymour Johns
 on Air Force Base (including a 21-gun salute)\, patriotic music performed b
 y the Brunswick Brass Band\, and a memorial wreath cast into the waters.\n\
 n2025 Military Guest Of Honor:\nGeneral Ralph J. Rizzo\, Jr.\, U.S. Marine 
 Corps\n\n2026 Date\n\n► Monday\, May 25\n\nThe public is invited to this fr
 ee observance.\n10am – Memorial Day Observance begins on the Battleship fan
 tail. \n\n► Fantail Observance is Weather Permitting.
DTEND:20260525T150000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030928Z
DTSTART:20260525T140000Z
