DESCRIPTION:Pack your picnic and enjoy iconic film music—from the triumphan
 t Chariots of Fire to the epic journey of The Lord of the Rings and the swe
 eping romance of Titanic—performed live in symphonic splendor. An unforgett
 able summer night of music\, movies\, and memories. \n\nSummerfest offers g
 reat music under the stars at Koka Booth Amphitheatre in Cary—and remember\
 , kids 12 & under are always admitted free on the lawn!\n\nNorth Carolina S
 ymphonyLawrence Loh\, conductor
