BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Education Programs,Lectures & Talks
DESCRIPTION:Its that time of year again! Come celebrate the summer at Merch
 ants Millpond State Park with our 4th year of the Summer Junior Adventure S
 eries! In this series\, we have a different topic that we teach about every
  Monday at 10 AM throughout the summer. \n\nThis week\, we will be looking 
 at the amazing world of Dragonflies! While these ariel predators are known 
 for their speed in the skies\, not many people know that their life begins 
 in the water. Come on out and join us as we learn more about what makes the
 se creatures so special. \n\nThis program will begin promptly at 10 AM at t
 he visitor center. All ages are welcome. Guests are encouraged to dress for
  the weather as we will be outside for part of this program.
DTEND:20260601T150000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030928Z
DTSTART:20260601T140000Z
GEO:36.437278;-76.701271
LOCATION:Merchants Millpond State Park\, Visitor Center
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Ranger Cody's Dashing Dragonflies
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_52558208387135
URL:https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/ranger-codys-dashing-dragonflies
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Celebrations & Commemorations
DESCRIPTION:Did you know that the Headquarters Library is almost 40 years o
 ld? Come to the library on Monday\, June 1st to celebrate the library's 40t
 h birthday! Look at the new mural on the side of the building to a celebrat
 ion of the library and 80s history! Light refreshments will be provided. \n
 \nThis project was produced with assistance from the America 250 North Caro
 lina initiative\, administered by the North Carolina Department of Natural 
 and Cultural Resources. Any opinions\, findings\, and conclusions or recomm
 endations expressed in this material are those of the author(s) and do not 
 necessarily reflect the views of the State of North Carolina
DTEND:20260601T210000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030928Z
DTSTART:20260601T190000Z
