DESCRIPTION:Step back in time and celebrate National Daniel Boone Day in th
 e town that bears his name! Join us at Hickory Ridge History Museum for a d
 ay filled with hands-on history\, living historical interpreters\, and colo
 nial craft demonstrations that bring the 18th century to life.\n\nExperienc
 e life on the frontier with:\n\nGuided tours of the museum’s six historic c
 abinsTraditional skills like blacksmithing\, hearth cooking\, and wool spin
 ningTomahawk throwing - test your frontier skills!Perfect for history lover
 s of all ages\, Dan’l Boone Day offers a unique opportunity to learn about 
 Boone’s legacy\, Appalachian traditions\, and the daily life of early settl
 ers.
