 C License - View Event. This workshop is open to those 12 years and older. 
 All minors must be accompanied by an adult.\n\nJoin our comprehensive Intro
 ductory Fishing Workshop designed to equip you with the essential skills an
 d knowledge for a successful start in fishing. NCWRC instructors will guide
  you through a variety of topics\, ensuring you feel confident and prepared
  for your fishing adventures.\n\nTopics Covered Include:\n\nLicensing & Reg
 ulationsEquipment & TackleFishing KnotsRigging and Bait SelectionFinding Fi
 shThis workshop includes both hands on classroom instruction and on-the-wat
 er fishing\, providing a well-rounded learning experience.
