DESCRIPTION:Join us for a FREE concert in Tarboro celebrating America 250 f
 eaturing patriotic favorites such as Sousa’s “The Stars and Stripes Forever
 \,” John Williams’ “Liberty Fanfare\,” the “Armed Forces Salute\,” and Copl
 and’s “Buckaroo Holiday.”\n\nNorth Carolina Symphony\nSophie Mok\, conducto
 r\n\nThis concert is FREE and open to the public. No tickets are required.
DTEND:20260610T011500Z
