DESCRIPTION:Learn about one of the small arms (musket\, flintlock\, or rifl
 e) that a soldier stationed at Fort Macon would have carried and used.\n\nT
 his will include a blank firing demonstration of the weapon.\nMeet in the f
 ort parade ground.\n\n \n\nPhoto by Jairus Hill : Living historian demonstr
 ating a musket at Fort Macon State Park.
