DESCRIPTION:Kitty Hawk Kites and friends will be displaying amazing patriot
 ic kites and inflatable animals on top of Jockey’s Ridge State Park. Join u
 s and fly a kite of your own\, take part in FREE walk-up stunt kite lessons
 \, kite coloring for kids of all ages\, or just sit back\, relax and enjoy 
 the spectacular kites as they fly in the sky.\n\n \n\nFor more information 
 on the Rogallo Kite Festival\, please contact events@kittyhawk.com\n\n \n\n
  \n\nPlease Remember: If you are going to join us on the dunes\, please bri
 ng enough water\, something to sit on\, and shade for you and your family i
 ncluding pets! Also wear comfortable clothing and appropriate shoe wear!
DTEND:20260612T200000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030929Z
DTSTART:20260612T140000Z
