BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Education Programs
DESCRIPTION:"Hey you guys!" Ready for a legendary treasure hunt? Join us at
  Museum for a special screening of the 80s adventure classic\, The Goonies.
 \n\n \n\nGather your crew\, grab some popcorn and relive the magic of One-E
 yed Willy’s hidden gold on the big screen. Before the movie\, explore the M
 useum’s own "hidden treasures" with themed activities that bring the movie’
 s mysteries to life.\n\n \n\nEvent Highlights:\n\n• Feature Film: The Gooni
 es (Rated PG)\n\n• Themed Fun: Hands-on science led by Museum experts.\n\n•
  Snacks: Grab your favorite movie treats.\n\n• Movie Trivia: Prove you’re a
  real Goonie and test your knowledge.\n\n \n\nGet Your Tickets: https://ncm
 ns.net/GooniesMovie\n\n \n\nDon't let the Fratellis beat you to it — mark y
 our calendars and get ready for an adventure!
DTEND:20260613T020000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030929Z
DTSTART:20260612T213000Z
GEO:35.782156;-78.639336
LOCATION:North Carolina Museum of Natural Sciences
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Museum Movie Night: The Goonies
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_52488054355575
URL:https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/museum-movie-night-the-goonies
END:VEVENT
