 on the Rogallo Kite Festival\, please contact events@kittyhawk.com\n\n \n\n
  \n\nPlease Remember: If you are going to join us on the dunes\, please bri
 ng enough water\, something to sit on\, and shade for you and your family i
 ncluding pets! Also wear comfortable clothing and appropriate shoe wear!
