DESCRIPTION:Join The Town of Seven Devils and a Park Ranger for this Great 
 Campout- Overnight Adventure. Learn how to pitch a tent\, build a campfire\
 , cook over a campfire\, and use Leave No Trace Principles all while enjoyi
 ng games and storytelling.\n\nDon't have any camping gear\, no problem! Ten
 ts\, sleeping bags\, and sleeping pads will be provided to use so any and a
 ll camping experiences are welcome! \n\n10 spots are available\, a chaperon
 e 18 years or older MUST accompany and camp overnight with the camper. Plea
 se email parksandrec@sevendevilsnc.gov to register. Please list any allergi
 es in your registration email as food and snacks will be provided.
