 ommemorations,Ceremonies & Anniversaries
DESCRIPTION:The North Carolina African American Heritage Commission is loan
 ing Lake Norman State Park their Oasis Spaces traveling exhibit.\n\nTo cont
 inue the celebrate Juneteenth all month long\, stop by our auditorium to le
 arn all about The Negro Motorist Green Book. Each display panel highlights 
 a North Carolina business owner and traveler.
DTEND:20260615T210000Z
