DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Knowing the West and the America 250 commemoration wi
 th a free\, family-friendly day of artmaking\, performances\, and community
  connection at the North Carolina Museum of Art. Enjoy hands-on art activit
 ies inspired by Western North Carolina craft traditions\, live music\, and 
 creative demonstrations from regional artists. Explore the exhibition Knowi
 ng the West through guided tours\, family-friendly activities\, and opportu
 nities to engage with artists and partners from across the state.
DTEND:20260627T200000Z
