BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Education Programs,Lectures & Talks
DESCRIPTION:Its that time of year again! Come celebrate the summer at Merch
 ants Millpond State Park with our 4th year of the Summer Junior Adventure S
 eries! In this series\, we have a different topic that we teach about every
  Monday at 10 AM throughout the summer. \n\nThis week we will go back in ti
 me to see some of the games that were played back in the era revolutionary 
 war in the U.S. with special guest star\, Amanda\, from Historic Edenton! A
 manda will take us through several fun games that kids played during the ti
 me. Come on out and experience a little bit of history as part of our A250 
 Celebration. \n\nThis program will start promptly at 10 AM at the visitor c
 enter. Guests are encouraged to dress for the weather as part of this progr
 am will be outside.
DTEND:20260629T150000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030930Z
DTSTART:20260629T140000Z
GEO:36.437278;-76.701271
LOCATION:Merchants Millpond State Park\, Visitor Center
