BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Outdoor & Recreation,Outdoor Recreation (kayak, paddle, hikes),E
 ducation Programs,Youth & Family Activities
DESCRIPTION:Join Us for the Jockey's Ridge Challenge!\n\nGet ready for an e
 xhilarating experience at Jockey's Ridge State Park as we proudly host the 
 Jockey's Ridge Challenge! This exciting event invites participants to run\,
  walk\, or overcome a thrilling 2-mile course on the tallest natural sand d
 une system in the eastern United States.\n\n \n\nWhether you're a seasoned 
 runner seeking a "unique" challenge or a walker looking to enjoy the stunni
 ng views\, this event is perfect for everyone! While the course promises a 
 competitive atmosphere\, it also welcomes those who want to take in the bre
 athtaking scenery at a more leisurely pace.\n\n \n\nBy participating\, you'
 ll be contributing to a worthy cause. Proceeds from the Jockey's Ridge Chal
 lenge will benefit Friends of Jockey's Ridge\, a local non-profit organizat
 ion dedicated to supporting\, preserving\, and enhancing Jockey's Ridge Sta
 te Park for future generations!\n\n \n\nTo honor our brave service members\
 , they will be offering a $5 discount for Active US Military and Veterans. 
 Join us for a day of fun\, fitness\, and community spirit at Jockey's Ridge
 !\n\nGeneral Pricing includes:\n\n2 Mile Dunes Race (Age 17 & Up) $55.00\n\
 n2 Mile Dunes Race (Age 10-16) $30.00\n\n1 Mile Color Run $30.00\n\n \n\nPl
 ease Note: On-site parking is limited\, so please carpool as much as possib
 le on race morning. A water station will be near the mid-point of the cours
 e. Dare County EMS will be on-call. While the exact course varies slightly 
 from year to year based on vegetation changes\, etc\, markings and guides w
 ill be visible throughout. Strollers and pets not allowed.
DTEND:20260703T130000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030931Z
DTSTART:20260703T120000Z
GEO:35.963597;-75.632255
LOCATION:Jockey's Ridge State Park
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Killer Dunes
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_52399397725168
URL:https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/killer-dunes
END:VEVENT
