DESCRIPTION:Liberty on Main is the City of Roanoke Rapids’ Independence Day
  celebration\, bringing together the community for a patriotic parade and d
 owntown festival on July 4\, 2026.\n\nThe day begins with a community parad
 e featuring local organizations\, businesses\, bands\, and first responders
 \, followed by a family-friendly festival with vendors\, activities\, and e
 ntertainment in the Main Street district.\n\nDesigned to create a welcoming
  and engaging experience for all ages\, Liberty on Main highlights communit
 y pride\, local participation\, and the shared traditions that bring people
  together.\n\nThis event brought to you by the City of Roanoke Rapids Main 
 Street Program and Advisory Committee.\n\nVendors and parade participants m
 ust register at MainStreetRoanokeRapids.com/250 by June 15\, 2026.
