DESCRIPTION:On July 4\, at 10 am\, the town of Mocksville will host a cerem
 ony to open the Mocksville Bicentennial Time Capsule. This capsule was dedi
 cated on December 12\, 1976\, which marked the end of the Bicentennial cele
 bration. Attendees will be allowed to witness the capsule's opening and to 
 see firsthand the items that have been buried within for the last forty-nin
 e and a half years. \n\nThe link to the event is listed below. Scroll down 
 until the subheading titled "Opening the Past: Mocksville’s Bicentennial Ti
 me Capsule" appears.
