DESCRIPTION:Celebrating Fourth of July in Onslow County\n\nOur Freedom Fest
  is the highlight of the summer! Thousands of attendees from all walks of l
 ife come together for live music\, foods for every taste\, and a spectacula
 r fireworks display. Attendees leave the event with nostalgia of an old fas
 hioned Independence Day celebration and pride for their community. In 2026\
 , America is celebrating its 250th birthday and the Freedom Festival will c
 elebrate this monumental occasion. \n\nThis year's event will take place on
  July 4th at Onslow Pines Park from 3-9PM. Join us for an unforgettable eve
 ning of music\, food trucks and fireworks. Open to the public\, no registra
 tion required.
DTEND:20260705T010000Z
