X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Performances & Arts,Concerts (Music),Celebrations & Commemoratio
 ns
DESCRIPTION:CELEBRATING MUSIC THROUGH 250 YEARS AND BEYOND!\n\nCelebrate th
 e Fourth of July with a spectacular family-friendly concert at the Live Oak
  Bank Pavilion\, featuring the Wilmington Symphony Orchestra (WSO) and spec
 ial guests.\n\nHighlights of the evening include guest appearances\, patrio
 tic favorites\, pops\, classics\, and spectacular fireworks display.\n\nFir
 eworks will start at 9:00 p.m.\, launched from a barge at the convergence o
 f the Cape Fear and Northeast Cape Fear Rivers\, just north of the park. Th
 is concert is FREE to attend!
DTEND:20260705T013000Z
