DESCRIPTION:Join the City of Sanford for a fun-filled evening at Red\, Whit
 e\, and Blue Bash as we celebrate Independence Day in style! Enjoy live per
 formances from incredible bands\, indulge in a variety of tasty treats from
  local food trucks\, and wrap up the night with a breathtaking fireworks sh
 ow. It's an event for all ages\, perfect for making memories with family an
 d friends as we come together to honor freedom and enjoy the summer night!
