BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Public Meetings,Organizational
DESCRIPTION:NC Public Librarian Certification Commission Meeting\n\nThe Nor
 th Carolina Public Librarian Certification Commission was formed in 1936 to
  set minimum standards for public librarians to protect and maintain public
  library resources\, to assure professional management and administration o
 f library services\, to meet the personnel requirements for State Aid admin
 istered by the State Library of NC\, and to guarantee the best possible pub
 lic library service to all North Carolinians. Commission meetings are held 
 quarterly to review applications and discuss Certification policies and pro
 cedures. \n\nFor information about the NC Public Librarian Certification Co
 mmission\, please visit https://slnc.info/PLCC.   \n\nDate/Time: \n\nApril 
 10\, 2026\, 1:00 pm - 4:00 pm\n\nJuly 10\, 2026\, 1:00 pm - 4:00 pm\n\nLoca
 tion:\n\nNC Department of Natural and Cultural Resources Building \nRoom 30
 8\n109 E. Jones St. \nRaleigh\, NC 27601
DTEND:20260710T200000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030932Z
DTSTART:20260710T170000Z
GEO:35.806063;-78.618252
LOCATION:North Carolina State Library of Accessible Books and Library Servi
 ces\, Room 308
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:NC Public Librarian Certification Commission Meeting
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_50585979700591
URL:https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/nc-public-librarian-certification-comm
 ission-meeting
END:VEVENT
