DESCRIPTION:Sidecar Social Club soars through numerous genres effortlessly 
 as their energetic set takes you from speakeasy jazz to cabarets. Move to t
 he sounds of Latin American dance halls\, the big band era\, and soulful R&
 B. \n\nThe orchestra will not be performing at this concert. \n\nPack your 
 picnic! Summerfest offers great music under the stars at Koka Booth Amphith
 eatre in Cary—and remember\, kids 12 & under are always admitted free on th
 e lawn!
