DESCRIPTION:Registration required at Go Outdoors website: North Carolina WR
 C License - View Event. This workshop is open to those 16 years and older. 
 All minors must be accompanied by an adult.\n\nAre you ready to dive into f
 ly-fishing but don’t know where to start? Join our ‘Before the Cast’ progra
 m and learn everything you need to confidently gear up for your next fishin
 g adventure!\n\nThis hands-on\, interactive class is perfect for beginners 
 and anyone looking to refine their understanding of fly-fishing gear. We’ll
  break down the fundamentals of selecting\, assembling\, and maintaining th
 e right equipment so you can fish effectively and enjoyably.
DTEND:20260719T160000Z
