DESCRIPTION:Join the North Carolina Wildlife Federation at Carolina Beach S
 tate Park for National Moth Week! Meet some moths you may have never seen b
 efore and listen for nocturnal birds in the coastal fringe forest of southe
 astern NC. Learn to use Seek and iNaturalist to identify and record species
  sightings. Upload 10 species observations to get your NC Moth Week badge!\
 n\nThis event is FREE and open to the public. Registration is required: htt
 ps://wl.donorperfect.net/weblink/weblink.aspx?name=E12185&id=1206
DTEND:20260725T020000Z
