BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Celebrations & Commemorations,Reenactments & Living History,Exhi
 bits & Tours,Special Site Programs
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we delve into the enlightenment age of dentistry!\n\
 nWithout its 18th century foundations\, dental chairs\, porcelain teeth\, m
 odern dentures\, and specific tools for dentists\, oral care would be much 
 worse! After this presentation\, you’ll want to give your dentist and denta
 l assistants a “plaque.”\n\nFind out the Tooth\, the Whole Tooth\, and noth
 ing by the Tooth on how our founding fathers took care of their oral hygien
 e and why we should be happy to have the dentists of today.\n\nThis event i
 s part of the museum’s Deep Dive Into History series\, programs designed to
  give visitors a deeper understanding of our shared past through costumed i
 nterpretation and hands-on learning. Each Deep Dive delves into a specific 
 theme in Lower Cape Fear history. This event is FREE\, but donations are al
 ways appreciated.
DTEND:20260725T190000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030932Z
DTSTART:20260725T150000Z
GEO:33.918176;-78.0178
LOCATION:North Carolina Maritime Museum at Southport
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:DEEP DIVE INTO HISTORY The Root of the Problem: 18th Century Dentis
 try
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_52072807372740
URL:https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/deep-dive-into-history-the-root-of-the
 -problem-18th-century-dentistry
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Education Programs,Lectures & Talks
DESCRIPTION:Have you heard of the Tory War? From 1780-81\, Cumberland Count
 y and the surrounding region fell into a civil war between Tories and Patri
 ots during the American Revolution. Learn the stories of courage and horror
  that took place in this formative period in the region's history!
DTEND:20260725T180000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030932Z
DTSTART:20260725T170000Z
GEO:35.055443;-78.881263
LOCATION:Cumberland County Headquarters Library
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:The Tory War
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51597001021499
URL:https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/the-tory-war
END:VEVENT
