DESCRIPTION:Come to Lake Norman's Visitor Center to see what our trucks loo
 k like! People will have a chance to step inside a Ranger's truck and see a
 ll the hats that Rangers wear on a day to day basis and we keep in our truc
 k to protect our visitors and park. \n\nThis event is to help celebrate Wor
 ld Ranger Day. \n\n \n\nPhoto by J. Davidson: A park ranger's flat hat with
  a scenic sunrise fall view at Morrow Mountain State Park
