BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Performances & Arts,Theater & Musicals
DESCRIPTION:Temple Theatre is one of North Carolina’s premier regional thea
 tres\, offering Broadway-quality productions in the heart of downtown Sanfo
 rd. In September\, Temple Theatre will present "1776: An American Musical\,
 " a stirring musical set in Philadelphia in 1776. \n\nTickets range from $2
 5 to $40 with discounts available for active military\, Lee County educator
 s and students\, and groups of 10 or more. Visit templeshows.org or call 91
 9-774-4512 for more information.
DTEND:20260910T190000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030933Z
DTSTART:20260910T180000Z
GEO:35.48114;-79.178793
LOCATION:Temple Theatre
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Temple Theatre Presents: "1776: An American Musical"
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51782323118271
URL:https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/temple-theatre-presents-1776-an-americ
 an-musical
END:VEVENT
