DESCRIPTION:Getting an education is more than “book learning” in school. Ho
 w to build\, craft\, and care for things to teach others is a form of educa
 tion too. Come see our costumed interpreters demonstrate some of the educat
 ional activities of the 18th and 19th centuries. FREE. All ages welcome. Dr
 op-in.
