BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Education Programs,Homeschool & Education Days
DESCRIPTION:Step back in time and experience life in the 18th century at Ho
 meschool and Family Day at Alamance Battleground! Designed especially for f
 amilies and homeschool groups\, this immersive event offers hands-on activi
 ties\, interactive programs\, and engaging historical demonstrations that b
 ring the past to life.
