BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Education Programs,Celebrations & Commemorations,Reenactments & 
 Living History,Exhibits & Tours,Special Site Programs,Youth & Family Activi
 ties
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the establishment of the Colonial Navy by the Contine
 ntal Congress on September 13\, 1775\, with demonstrations of all things na
 val: ropemaking\, signal flags\, maps\, naval stores\, spinning and weaving
 \, blacksmithing. Learn about Bath and its role in the naval life of the co
 lony. Munitions demonstrations scheduled throughout the day.
DTEND:20260912T190000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030933Z
DTSTART:20260912T140000Z
GEO:35.476994;-76.811651
LOCATION:Historic Bath
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Our Maritime Heritage. Living History at Bath – 
