BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Celebrations & Commemorations,Reenactments & Living History,Exhi
 bits & Tours,Special Site Programs,Education Programs,Youth & Family Activi
 ties
DESCRIPTION:Experience life in the Southern Appalachian backcountry during 
 the American Revolution at our Militia Muster! Guests of all ages are invit
 ed to step into the world of 18th-century militia life through interactive 
 demonstrations\, reenactments\, and hands-on activities.\n\nWatch as 18th C
 entury Militia reenactors bring history to life through drills\, camp life\
 , and mock recruitment scenes. Explore the daily challenges faced by settle
 rs and soldiers\, and learn more about what it took to fight for independen
 ce in the mountains of North Carolina.\n\nThis is a family-friendly\, immer
 sive educational event perfect for history lovers\, homeschool families\, a
 nd curious visitors of all ages.\n\nPlease call 828-264-2120 for ticketing 
 information.
DTEND:20260919T180000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030934Z
DTSTART:20260919T150000Z
GEO:36.208683;-81.669982
LOCATION:Hickory Ridge History Museum
SEQUENCE:0
