 bits & Tours,Special Site Programs
DESCRIPTION:Join us at Fort Fisher State Historic Site for our annual\, day
 -long event about the WWII experience at Fort Fisher on October 3rd\, 2026!
 \n\nGeneral admission is FREE\, no tickets required for entry. Doors open a
 t 9:00am and close at 5:00pm. Public programs will be held between 10:00am 
 and 4:00pm.\n\nMore information about these programs will be provided in th
 e coming months. Stay tuned to the NC DNCR Events Calendar and Fort Fisher'
 s social media as we approach October 3!
DTEND:20261003T200000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030934Z
DTSTART:20261003T140000Z
GEO:33.971637;-77.91773
LOCATION:Fort Fisher Historic Site
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Fort Fisher's Second World War
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51781004638012
