BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Celebrations & Commemorations,Festivals & Fairs
DESCRIPTION:Experience the magic of MumFest\, a delightful fall festival in
  historic downtown New Bern! Enjoy live music\, thrilling amusements\, deli
 cious food\, unique local artists and vendors\, and a fantastic beer garden
  - all set against a stunning waterfront background. With over 75\,000 atte
 ndees last year\, this unforgettable weekend is the perfect way to celebrat
 e the season with family and friends. Mark your calendars now - come join t
 he fun!
DTEND:20261011T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030934Z
DTSTART:20261010T140000Z
