DESCRIPTION:Join us at Brunswick Town/Fort Anderson State Historic Site for
  the return of Port Brunswick Day! Living historians will be interpreting v
 arious colonial trades and aspects of colonial life\, including candle maki
 ng\, blacksmithing\, woodworking\, and more. Kids will have an opportunity 
 to experience colonial toys and games. This event is free. All ages are wel
 come.
