BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:
DESCRIPTION:BOO! EEEEKKKK! It's spooky season yet again! \n\nUsing our flas
 hlights\, we will search through the woods to find hidden nocturnal animals
  and listen for the creepy sounds that they make at night. Costumes are wel
 come and candy will be handed out at the end of the hike. \n\nThis hike can
  be selfled or a Ranger led hike will begin at 6:30 pm.
DTEND:20261023T233000Z
