DESCRIPTION:Dive into a variety of STEAM displays and demonstrations across
  the site. The highlight of the day is a unique opportunity to step into th
 e shoes of historic miners as you explore 450 feet of restored tunnels\, 50
  feet below the surface\, in our underground mine.\n\nAdmission is $4.00 (p
 lus tax) for ages 5 and up and children under 5 are free of charge. Cash an
 d credit card payments inside the Visitor Center (we cannot accept American
  Express).\n\nGold panning will be offered\, weather permitting\, for an ad
 ditional $4.00 per person (plus tax). \n\nRegistration is not accepted for 
 Homeschool Day.
DTEND:20261106T190000Z
