DESCRIPTION:Learn how early Americans prepared and cooked for large dinner 
 parties like what most of us experience during the Thanksgiving holiday. Ou
 r costumed interpreters will demonstrate how to cook a fall harvest meal ov
 er an open hearth in the Hoggatt House. Food samples are unavailable to the
  public. Demonstration only. FREE. All ages welcome. Drop-in.
