BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Exhibits & Tours,Special Site Programs
DESCRIPTION:Experience an authentic Christmas of long ago in the warm glow 
 of lantern light.  Enjoy homes\, public buildings\, and taverns decorated f
 or the season with festive\, all-natural décor.  Interactive historical vig
 nettes will bring each building to life.  Enjoy a warm fire in the Tap Room
  tavern\, just as guests did two hundred years ago! Tickets go on sale Nov.
  1st.  \n\n \n\nFee\, ticket required.
DTEND:20261205T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T030935Z
DTSTART:20261204T230000Z
