BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Celebrations & Commemorations,Reenactments & Living History
DESCRIPTION:Come enjoy the beauty of a 19th century Christmas aglow with ca
 ndlelight. This holiday season\, you are invited to tour the home of John a
 nd Amy Harper decorated for Christmas. Enjoy period music\, cider by a warm
  fire\, a festive wagon ride\, a soldiers camp\, plus crafts and activities
 . Do not miss your chance to experience Christmas by candlelight at Bentonv
 ille Battlefield!
